                        <interp inst="t18390204-name-1464" type="surname" value="BARLOW"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18390204-name-1464" type="given" value="JAMES"></interp>JAMES BARLOW</persName>
                  </hi>. I am foreman-millwright at the London Docks. I consider this cap belongs to the Docks—I had missed two caps the day be<lb></lb>fore, and that day I missed one.</p>
